12:50.200 --> 12:52.372
в™Є OOGA SHAKA, OOGA OOGA в™Є

12:52.372 --> 12:54.244
в™Є OOGA SHAKA, OOGA OOGA в™Є

12:54.244 --> 12:56.476
в™Є OOGA SHAKA, OOGA OOGA в™Є
I CAN'T STOP THIS FEELING.

12:56.476 --> 12:58.778
в™Є I CAN'T STOP THIS FEELING в™Є

12:58.778 --> 13:00.510
DEEP INSIDE OF ME.

13:00.510 --> 13:02.482
в™Є DEEP INSIDE OF ME в™Є

13:02.482 --> 13:05.455
JULES, I DON'T THINK YOU
REALIZE WHAT YOU DO TO ME.

13:05.455 --> 13:10.090
в™Є GIRL, YOU JUST DON'T REALIZE
WHAT YOU DO TO ME в™Є

13:10.090 --> 13:11.121
в™Є OOGA OOGA в™Є

13:11.121 --> 13:12.792
в™Є OOGA SHAKA, OOGA OOGA в™Є

13:12.792 --> 13:16.326
в™Є WHEN YOU HOLD ME
IN YOUR ARMS SO TIGHT в™Є

13:16.326 --> 13:21.331
в™Є YOU LET ME KNOW,
EVERYTHING'S ALL RIGHT в™Є

13:21.331 --> 13:26.436
в™Є I-I-I-I'M HOOKED
