13:28.438 --> 13:32.182
в™Є I'M HIGH ON BELIEVING в™Є

13:32.182 --> 13:36.486
в™Є THAT YOU'RE IN LOVE WITH ME в™Є

13:36.486 --> 13:39.189
[ MARCHING BAND PLAYS
"HOOKED ON A FEELING" ]

13:59.839 --> 14:01.341
[ CLANGS ]

14:01.341 --> 14:04.614
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO CA--
HE WAS SUPPOSED TO CATCH THAT.

14:04.614 --> 14:06.316
Woman: OH!

14:07.617 --> 14:10.250
[ CROWD MURMURS ]

14:11.621 --> 14:13.253
JULES COBB...

14:13.253 --> 14:14.384
YEAH?

14:14.384 --> 14:17.157
...WILL YOU MARRY ME?

14:17.157 --> 14:18.558
[ ALL GASP ]

14:21.061 --> 14:22.332
OKAY!

14:22.332 --> 14:24.194
SHE SAID YES!
WE'RE GETTING MARRIED!

14:24.194 --> 14:27.267
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

14:30.100 --> 14:32.442
WHAT'D I MISS?

14:33.904 --> 14:36.907
DUDE! EPIC FLASH MOB!
WHOO!

14:36.907 --> 14:39.449
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

14:41.211 --> 14:42.882
ANYBODY ELSE WANT SOME WINE?

14:42.882 --> 14:44.314
I THINK I'M GOOD.

14:44.314 --> 14:46.556
THE CHAMPAGNE WAS REALLY FLOWING
AT YOUR ENGAGEMENT.

14:46.556 --> 14:49.389
I KNOW!
SAM THOUGHT OF EVERYTHING.

14:51.221 --> 14:52.662
DUDE, LIGHTEN UP.
OKAY.

14:52.662 --> 14:55.926
SORRY I ACCIDENTALLY SAID
"YES" TO A WEDDING PROPOSAL.

14:55.926 --> 14:58.368
THE GREATEST PROPOSAL
OF ALL TIME,

14:58.368 --> 15:00.971
ACCORDING
TO THE ENTIRE INTERNET.

15:00.971 --> 15:03.073
YOU KNOW WHAT? SAM IS NOT JUST
HANDSOME AND CHARMING.

15:03.073 --> 15:05.005
HE IS CRAZY RICH.

15:05.005 --> 15:07.107
OOH, WELL, TOO BAD
YOU'RE CRAZY MARRIED.

15:07.107 --> 15:09.039
WOULD YOU TELL HER
HOW NUTS THIS IS?

15:09.039 --> 15:10.340
I CAN'T HELP YOU THERE.

15:10.340 --> 15:12.482
JUST WATCHING THIS
MAKES ME OVULATE.

15:12.482 --> 15:15.385
JUST THE SIGHT OF THAT RING
INCINERATED MY UNDERWEAR.

15:15.385 --> 15:16.586
WHAT?

15:16.586 --> 15:18.548
OH, GOOD.
YOU STILL HAVE IT ON.

15:18.548 --> 15:20.020
MY HAND FELT NAKED,

15:20.020 --> 15:22.052
AND MY REAL WEDDING RING
GOT LOST IN THE CAR.

15:22.052 --> 15:23.193
WELL,
DID YOU LOOK FOR IT?

15:23.193 --> 15:25.295
OH, WELL, I'M GOING TO.

15:25.295 --> 15:26.696
ALL RIGHT, BABE.

15:26.696 --> 15:29.129
YOU KNOW I GET SWEPT UP
IN EXCITING MOMENTS.

15:29.129 --> 15:31.101
BY THE TIME I REALIZED
WHAT I HAD DONE,

15:31.101 --> 15:32.932
I HAD A HUNDRED PEOPLE
IN MY FACE.

15:32.932 --> 15:35.005
AND I WAS TOO EMBARRASSED
TO OWN UP TO IT.

15:35.005 --> 15:36.406
I'M GONNA HAVE DINNER
WITH SAM TONIGHT

15:36.406 --> 15:37.968
AND I'M GONNA TELL HIM
THE TRUTH.

15:37.968 --> 15:41.071
I JUST COULD NOT HUMILIATE HIM
IN FRONT OF A CROWD.

15:41.071 --> 15:44.344
FINE, TELL HIM TONIGHT.

15:44.344 --> 15:46.346
AND TAKE THAT RING OFF
IN OUR HOUSE!

15:46.346 --> 15:48.348
I WAS JUST ABOUT TO!

15:48.348 --> 15:50.380
I WASN'T.
THIS THING IS GORGEOUS!

15:50.380 --> 15:51.721
YOU ARE SO LUCKY!

15:51.721 --> 15:53.123
SO BEAUTIFUL!

15:53.123 --> 15:54.985
I HAVE A LOT TO DO
BEFORE DINNER.

15:54.985 --> 15:57.957
YOU KNOW, I HAVEN'T HAD A REASON
TO SHAVE MY LEGS IN WEEKS!

15:57.957 --> 16:01.431
YOU SEE, THIS STORY
SOUNDS CRAZY,

16:01.431 --> 16:05.295
BUT WE HAVE A VIDEO THAT
PROVES IT'S NOT A HUGE LIE.

16:05.295 --> 16:07.567
[ SCOFFS ]
WHAT?
WHY ARE YOU SO UPSET?

16:07.567 --> 16:11.601
I MIGHT HAVE GOTTEN A COUNTRY
WRONG, BUT I WASN'T LYING.

16:11.601 --> 16:14.274
ELLIE, I JUST HATE THAT
IT'S SO IMPORTANT TO YOU

16:14.274 --> 16:15.575
TO DESTROY MY CREDIBILITY.

16:18.108 --> 16:19.549
OH, POOR THING.

16:19.549 --> 16:22.112
YOU KNOW WHAT SHE NEEDS
IS A HUG FROM SAM.

16:22.112 --> 16:24.614
HE GAVE ME A HUG.
I POPPED A WOODROW.

16:26.486 --> 16:28.688
PREPPING FOR
GOLF-CART JOUSTING?
Bobby: NO.

16:28.688 --> 16:32.722
BUT THAT IS AN AWESOME IDEA
THAT WE ARE TOTALLY GONNA TRY!

16:32.722 --> 16:35.465
WHEN WE GET THE PIZZA SCOOP
ON THE GOLF CART,

16:35.465 --> 16:38.098
BOBBY WILL BE THE ONLY
SNOW PLOWER IN TOWN!

16:38.098 --> 16:39.399
CHA-CHING!

16:39.399 --> 16:40.700
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

16:42.432 --> 16:43.703
OKAY, WELL, THIS IS INSANE.

16:43.703 --> 16:45.475
SO I'M GONNA SET THINGS
STRAIGHT.

16:45.475 --> 16:48.208
I CAN'T WATCH YOU
KILL HIS DREAMS!

16:48.208 --> 16:49.709
DAD, I HATE TO DO THIS,

16:49.709 --> 16:52.112
BUT I'D RATHER YOU ACCEPT IT NOW
THAN BE CRUSHED TOMORROW.

16:52.112 --> 16:53.743
YOU'RE NOT GONNA WAKE UP
TO SNOW.

16:53.743 --> 16:55.715
IT'S NOT COLD ENOUGH.

16:55.715 --> 16:57.417
[ SIGHS ]

16:57.417 --> 17:01.151
YEAH, MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.
I JUST WANTED IT SO BAD.

17:01.151 --> 17:02.722
IT'S NOT EVEN CHILLY.

17:02.722 --> 17:05.125
HEY, THANKS
FOR THE TOUGH LOVE, SON.

17:06.456 --> 17:09.359
NOW I JUST GOT TO FIND A WAY
TO BREAK IT TO DOG TRAVIS.

17:11.331 --> 17:13.303
[ SIGHS ]
HEY, PAL.

17:13.303 --> 17:15.565
YOU KNOW HOW YOU WERE
ALL EXCITED AND STUFF

17:15.565 --> 17:16.636
TO SEE SNOW?

17:18.438 --> 17:21.511
[ Voice breaking ] DO YOU HAVE
ANY IDEA HOW HARD THIS IS?

17:23.443 --> 17:25.645
YOU KNOW, THIS MAY SOUND
STRANGE FOR ME TO SAY,

17:25.645 --> 17:27.577
BUT THANKS FOR AT LEAST
DOING THIS HERE AT MY BAR

17:27.577 --> 17:29.079
WHERE I CAN SEE IT.

17:29.079 --> 17:30.780
OH, HONEY.
I WOULD BE A CRAPPY WIFE

17:30.780 --> 17:33.623
IF I DIDN'T LET MY HUSBAND
COME TO MY ENGAGEMENT DINNER.

17:33.623 --> 17:36.486
I PROMISE AS SOON AS I HAVE
SOME PRIVACY WITH SAM,

17:36.486 --> 17:37.587
I'M GONNA TELL HIM.

17:38.728 --> 17:41.091
THERE SHE IS,
THE FUTURE MRS. JOHNSTON.

17:41.091 --> 17:42.692
THAT'S YOU
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

17:42.692 --> 17:44.194
MY LAST NAME IS JOHNSTON.

17:44.194 --> 17:45.695
OH, I LIKE IT.

17:45.695 --> 17:47.237
HEY, SHOULD I GO BY J.J.?

17:47.237 --> 17:48.268
NO!
AAH! GOD!

17:48.268 --> 17:49.799
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

17:49.799 --> 17:54.604
OH, UM, SAM, THIS IS, UM,
NEIGHBOR, FRIEND GRAYSON.

17:54.604 --> 17:56.346
NEIGHBOR-FRIEND GRAYSON.
NICE TO MEET YOU.

17:56.346 --> 17:58.208
I'M IN REALLY GOOD SHAPE.

17:58.208 --> 18:00.310
OKAY, I'LL, UH, TRY
TO SPREAD THE WORD.

18:00.310 --> 18:03.082
SAM, CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A SECOND?

18:03.082 --> 18:04.454
YEAH.

18:04.454 --> 18:07.587
UM, LISTEN.
I MADE A BIG MISTAKE.

18:07.587 --> 18:09.759
NO, NO, NO.
I MADE A BIG MISTAKE.

18:09.759 --> 18:13.092
TO AMBUSH YOU IN FRONT
OF A HUNDRED OF MY FRIENDS...

18:13.092 --> 18:14.794
AND NONE OF MY FAMILY!

18:14.794 --> 18:17.497
MOM, DAD, GRANDMA!

18:17.497 --> 18:19.669
GET IN HERE!
THIS IS JULES!

18:19.669 --> 18:20.800
OHH, HONEY!

18:20.800 --> 18:22.772
[ ALL TALKING EXCITEDLY ]

18:22.772 --> 18:24.204
Jules: OH, THANK YOU.

18:24.204 --> 18:27.777
HOW IS IT THAT NO ONE
HAS SNATCHED HER UP?

18:27.777 --> 18:29.239
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

18:29.239 --> 18:31.541
IT'S ALMOST IMPOSSIBLE
TO BELIEVE.

18:31.541 --> 18:33.313
Laurie: OH, GOOD.

18:33.313 --> 18:34.844
DID YOU COME
TO TELL EVERYONE

18:34.844 --> 18:36.786
THAT THIS ISN'T
MY REAL HAIR COLOR?

18:36.786 --> 18:38.418
I THINK THEY ALREADY KNOW.

18:38.418 --> 18:42.452
ACTUALLY, I, UM -- I BROUGHT YOU
A LITTLE SOMETHING.

18:42.452 --> 18:45.195
[ GASPS ] MISSY!
YOU FREELOADING BITCH!

18:45.195 --> 18:46.796
YOU OWE ME 20 BUCKS!

18:46.796 --> 18:48.828
WHY DON'T YOU COME AND GET IT,
YOU OVER-BLEACHED SKANK?!

18:48.828 --> 18:50.330
I'M GONNA RIP OFF YOUR FACE

18:50.330 --> 18:52.402
AND I'M GONNA SHOVE IT
UP YOUR CORN CHUTE!

18:52.402 --> 18:53.733
THAT'LL BE ALL, MISSY.

18:53.733 --> 18:55.765
[ SCOFFS ]

18:55.765 --> 18:57.267
THANK YOU.

18:58.668 --> 19:00.210
HEY, LAURIE.
DID YOU DYE YOUR HAIR?

19:00.210 --> 19:01.671
BITE ME, LITTLE EYES!

19:03.273 --> 19:04.514
[ SCOFFS ]

19:04.514 --> 19:06.276
OKAY, WHY DID YOU
BRING HER HERE?

19:06.276 --> 19:07.577
TO PROVE A POINT.

19:07.577 --> 19:09.419
I SPENT FIVE HOURS TODAY

19:09.419 --> 19:12.782
LOOKING FOR SOMEONE
I WASN'T EVEN SURE EXISTED.

19:12.782 --> 19:16.356
BUT I KEPT LOOKING
BECAUSE I BELIEVE YOU.

19:16.356 --> 19:19.789
IT'S TOUGH FOR ME TO ACCEPT
ALL THE THINGS YOU SAY,

19:19.789 --> 19:22.462
BUT DEEP DOWN, I KNOW THAT
YOU'RE AN HONEST PERSON.

19:22.462 --> 19:23.933
THANK YOU, ELLIE.

19:23.933 --> 19:26.766
THAT REALLY
MEANS A LOT TO ME.

19:28.238 --> 19:30.540
CHECK IT.
TEAM SAM.

19:30.540 --> 19:32.642
WHO'S WITH ME?

19:32.642 --> 19:34.374
Oh, this is
a complete disaster!

19:34.374 --> 19:36.506
I just didn't want
to publicly humiliate him!

19:36.506 --> 19:37.877
I KNOW. BUT UNLESS

19:37.877 --> 19:39.579
YOU WANT TO GO AHEAD
AND ACTUALLY MARRY THE GUY --

19:39.579 --> 19:41.211
THAT WOULD GET ME
OFF THE HOOK.
NO, LISTEN.

19:41.211 --> 19:43.182
THE ONLY WAY OUT OF THIS
IS TO TELL HIM.

19:43.182 --> 19:44.484
I KNOW.

19:44.484 --> 19:46.386
BUT I JUST HATE
TO DISAPPOINT PEOPLE,

19:46.386 --> 19:47.887
AND EVERYONE HERE'S
GONNA HATE ME.

19:47.887 --> 19:50.760
OKAY.
I KNOW I HAVE TO DO IT.

19:50.760 --> 19:51.921
SAM?

19:51.921 --> 19:53.393
YEAH.

19:53.393 --> 19:54.724
I HAVE SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU.

19:54.724 --> 19:56.466
OH!

19:56.466 --> 19:59.869
EVERYONE, MY FIANCГ©E HAS
AN ANNOUNCEMENT TO MAKE!

19:59.869 --> 20:01.531
NO. NO,
THAT'S NOT WHAT I MEANT.

20:01.531 --> 20:04.334
OKAY.

20:04.334 --> 20:06.306
WHAT THE HECK.

20:06.306 --> 20:07.807
UM...
ALL RIGHT.

20:07.807 --> 20:10.340
SAM,
YOU ARE AN AMAZING GUY.

20:10.340 --> 20:12.242
AND YOU HAVE
AN AMAZING FAMILY.

20:12.242 --> 20:15.615
AND THAT'S WHY, UH, THIS
IS SO DIFFICULT FOR ME.

20:15.615 --> 20:17.247
ALL RIGHT! STOP!

20:17.247 --> 20:20.820
I CAN'T STAND TO HEAR
ANOTHER SECOND OF THIS!

20:20.820 --> 20:24.254
JULES...
I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU!

20:24.254 --> 20:26.496
I'VE BEEN IN LOVE WITH YOU
SINCE THE MOMENT I SAW YOU.

20:26.496 --> 20:28.298
AND I'VE JUST BEEN TOO SCARED
TO SAY IT.

20:28.298 --> 20:30.500
BUT NOW SAM HERE WITH HIS
LIVE-FOR-THE-MOMENT SPIRIT

20:30.500 --> 20:33.263
HAS INSPIRED ME TO DO THIS.

20:33.263 --> 20:36.366
JULES...
[ GASPS ]

20:36.366 --> 20:39.809
DON'T MARRY HIM.
MARRY ME.

20:39.809 --> 20:42.742
HE'S PROPOSING WITHOUT JUGGLERS?
[ SCOFFS ]

20:42.742 --> 20:44.414
THIS IS A TOTAL SHOCK!

20:44.414 --> 20:46.646
I HAD NO IDEA
YOU FELT THIS WAY,

20:46.646 --> 20:48.348
AND...I FEEL IT, TOO!

20:48.348 --> 20:49.749
SO, YES, I WILL MARRY YOU!

20:49.749 --> 20:52.922
BOO!
WRONG CHOICE.

20:52.922 --> 20:55.285
I'M SO SORRY, SAM.

20:55.285 --> 20:57.887
IT'S JUST THAT I'VE BEEN IN LOVE
WITH GRAYSON FOR YEARS.

20:57.887 --> 21:01.260
AND I JUST NEVER REALIZED IT
UNTIL THIS VERY MOMENT.

21:01.260 --> 21:03.793
I WISH YOU'D REALIZED IT
YESTERDAY

21:03.793 --> 21:05.665
BEFORE I SPENT $200,000.

21:05.665 --> 21:07.367
[ COUGHS ]
TWO--

21:07.367 --> 21:09.999
I MEAN, ON THE ONE HAND,
I ADMIRE WHAT GRAYSON'S DOING,

21:09.999 --> 21:11.571
AND ON THE OTHER HAND, CRAP!

21:11.571 --> 21:13.843
OH, SAM,
YOU'RE AN INCREDIBLE GUY.

21:13.843 --> 21:16.275
YOU'RE GONNA FIND
SOMEONE AMAZING

21:16.275 --> 21:18.448
WHO DESERVES YOU
MORE THAN I DO.

21:18.448 --> 21:21.010
A FEW MINUTES AGO, I HAD IT ALL.

21:21.010 --> 21:25.485
AND NOW I'M JUST
A LONELY BILLIONAIRE.

21:25.485 --> 21:28.758
HI, THERE.
I'M MISSY.

21:28.758 --> 21:31.691
YOU KNOW, I FEEL AS THOUGH
THIS COULD END IN BREAKFAST

21:31.691 --> 21:35.465
FOR THE TWO OF US
IF YOU'RE INTERESTED.

21:35.465 --> 21:38.568
REMEMBER WHEN I SAID
I WAS LONELY BEFORE?

21:38.568 --> 21:39.629
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

21:43.373 --> 21:45.335
WHAT THE...?

21:45.335 --> 21:47.036
Bobby: IT'S ON! IT'S ON!

21:50.580 --> 21:52.311
SNOW!

21:52.311 --> 21:54.884
в™Є WHEREVER YOU ARE в™Є
YOU DID THIS?

21:54.884 --> 21:58.418
WELL, SOMEBODY HAD TO KEEP
BOBBY'S DREAM ALIVE.

21:58.418 --> 22:00.990
SEE, TRAV? I TOLD YOU
I'D WAKE UP TO SNOW!

22:00.990 --> 22:03.423
WELL, IT DIDN'T SNOW.
THIS IS...

22:04.754 --> 22:06.856
...SNOW.
YOU WERE RIGHT, DAD.

22:06.856 --> 22:08.558
THE POWER
OF POSITIVE THINKING --

22:08.558 --> 22:09.629
